      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Utij Ziana! iſbehds/ kaſ tu\npee tahs Babeles Meitasdsihwo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Jo ta fakka tas KUNGS\nZebnot: Pehz tahs Gohdibas irr\nwiꞥſch manni juhtijs pee teem\nPagakeem/ kaſ juhs irr aplau-\npiſcht/ jo kaſ juhs aiſkarx/ tas\naiſkarx winna AzRaugu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Jo reds/ Es kustinatchu\nfawu Rohku pahr teem/ tee buhs\natweem Kalpeem par Laupitcha-\nnu/ ta fajuttifeet juhs/ ka tas\nKUNGS Zebact manni irr\njuhtijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Gawile/ un preezajecs tu\nZianas Meita/ jo raugi/ Es\nnahfu un dsihwoschu tawa Wid-\ndū/ fakka tas KUNGS:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un dands Pagani taps\ntai Deenā tam KUNGA M\nveepulzeti/ un tee buhs man par\nLaudim/ un es dsihwoschu tawa\nWiddū/ un tu fajuttifi/ ka tas\nKUNGS Zebact manni pee te-\nvim irr juhtijs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Tad eemantohs tas\nKUNGS Inhdn par fawu\nTeeju eeſsch tahs fwehtas Sem-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Zeeti kluffu wiffa Meefa\npreekſch ta KUNGA. Jo wiꞥſch\nirr uhēmohdees no tawas fweh-\ntas Weetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta III. Nodalla.\nJosuus tas angsts Preesteris klubſt pee ta\nDeewa Mamma Uhſzelfchanas eepreezi-\nnahts: 1. Ka tas KUNGS winnu par\njaweem Eenaidneekem apsargabs: 2. Wiꞥ-\nnam tohp arridsan apfohlihts tas Zemak/\ntas irr Kristus: 3.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "1. Ehz to rahdija wiꞥſch\nBman Josuu to angstu\nPreestert preekſch ta\nKUNGA Engeta stahwain.\nUn tas Satans stahweja pa\nwinna labbas Rohkas winnam\nprettiturredamess.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "2. Bet tas KUNGS tazzija\nuhs to Satanu: Lai tas KUNGS\ntewi lamina Satans/ kaſ Jeru-\nsalemi irr iſwehlejs. Neggi\nſchis irr weena Pagale no ta\nUgguns afsgrabbta?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "3. Un Josuus bij apgehrbts\nar neschkibstahin Drehbehin/ kad\nwiꞥſch preekſch ta Engeta stah-\nweja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "4. Tad atbildēja wiꞥſch/ un\nrunnaja us teem/ kaſ preekſch\nwinna stahweja/ un fazztia:\nAtneimmeet schahs neschkibstas\nDrebbes no winna nobst. Pehz\nto fazzija wiꞥſch uhs to: Redz/\nEs eſimu taiwu Noseegunu no\nferum atnehnis/ un aptwillſchu\ntewi ar Swehtku Drehbehin.\n"
    }
  ],
